# Test Requirements

Every feature must include tests for every layer touched.

| Stack | Required tests |
|-------|----------------|
| KMP | Unit tests, ViewModel tests, repository tests |
| Backend | Unit tests, integration tests (table-driven where applicable) |
| Next.js | Component tests, API/route tests |

# Validation Commands

Run applicable commands after every implementation. Fix failures and repeat until green.

## KMP (from `mobile/`)

```bash
./gradlew ktlintCheck
./gradlew test
./gradlew build
```

## Backend (from `backend/` or `services/backend/` when present)

```bash
go fmt ./...
go test ./...
golangci-lint run
```

## Next.js (from `web/`)

```bash
npm run lint
npm run test
npm run build
```

# Fix-Until-Green Loop

1. Run validation for every stack you modified.
2. If any command fails, fix the issue.
3. Run validation again.
4. Repeat until all commands pass.
5. Never mark work complete with failing tests or builds.
